Translation: Active orders are issued directly by you through the tools. There is a limit of active orders you can issue depending on the amount of Memory resources your Ship Computer has at any given time. If you issue more orders than your Ship Computer can handle, you will have to wait for the active order count to go down before issuing new orders.
